## [0.3.0] (backend 0.7.0) - 2016-09-23

### Added

- Windows release.
- Enable to create drive.
- Add in-app notifications.

### Changed

- Use backend 0.7.0.
- Optimize asynchronous calls.

### Fixed

- Pass private inputs through a stream.
- Make sure the permission window only spawn once.
- Behave nicely if a part of a drive is missing (network or volume).

