## [0.2.1] (backend 0.5.2) - 2016-02-29

### Fixed

- Fix mount / unmount button not changing state.
- Change the invitation popup to cover the whole window.
- Report the correct error if uploading an avatar fails.
- Fix error reporting on login.

### Changed

- Use backend 0.5.2.
- Show only drives you own or you have been invited to.
- Automatically open mountpoint after mounting a drive.

## [0.2.0] (backend 0.5.0) - 2016-02-24

### Added

- Add email confirmation screen.

### Changed

- Use backend 0.5.0.
- Show invitation individually.
- Show mount / unmount buttons on the main view.
- Turn update banner to a smaller alert message.

### Removed

- Remove detailed drive view.
